{
  "id": "RAW_387ca7",
  "title": "李飞飞最新访谈：追逐 AI 的“北极星”—从 ImageNet 到三维世界的空间智能 |附全文+视频",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIxODUzNTg2MA==&mid=2247488684&idx=1&sn=74f563a62ef98b90dbb15f28be7cf8c1",
  "date": "2025-07-02 07:28:00",
  "author": "Web3天空之城",
  "siteName": "Web3天空之城",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <p><span style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight: bold; background-color: inherit; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.1em;\">Web3天空之城·城主：</span></p><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);color: rgb(10, 10, 10);font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;\">\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px 8px 1.5em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">李飞飞博士（Fei-Fei Li）无论在美国还是国内，都是一颗耀眼的AI“北极星”。她曾以ImageNet项目引爆了深度学习的数据革命，被誉为“AI教母”。这位顶尖科学家再次设定了一个宏大的目标：构建理解和交互三维世界的“空间智能”，并为此创立了World Labs。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px 8px 1.5em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">最近李飞飞参加了YC创业学院的现场论坛， 她的现场访谈今日最新被发布。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">“</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">我整个职业生涯都在追逐那些极其困难，近乎妄想的问题。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">”李飞飞在最近一次深入访谈中坦陈，“</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">对我来说，没有空间智能的AGI是不完整的。我想解决这个问题。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">”她的职业生涯，从一位不谙英语的移民少年，到经营自助洗衣店，再到成为斯坦福大学人工智能教授、谷歌云AI首席科学家，直至今日投身创业，都贯彻着一种“智识上的无畏”和“</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">埋头苦干，努力建设。那是我的舒适区</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">”的企业家精神。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">关于李飞飞的空间智能方向，可以想到的是，当年做ImageNet的时候，恐怕没一个人看好她。而这次，如果真的解决了AI对于3维空间的理解， 说不定就是AGI突破的契机呢。</span></p>\n   <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n   <div></div>\n   <p></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\">核心观点摘要</span></h3>\n   <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">ImageNet的范式转变：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">“这是一个数据驱动的范式转变，而且这个范式转变必须由数据驱动的方法来领导。它确实是数据、GPU和神经网络结合在一起的最初时刻。”</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">空间智能是AI的下一个前沿：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">“从根本上说，语言是一维的……世界远比这复杂。首先，真实世界是3D的。”“对我来说，没有空间智能的通用人工智能（AGI）是不完整的。”</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">智识上的无畏：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">“我的整个职业生涯都在追逐那些非常困难、近乎妄想的问题……那种勇气，那种拥抱困难的无畏精神，并着手去做，全身心投入，以任何你想要的方式去解决它，这确实是成功人士的核心特征。”</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">创业精神的本质：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">“我只是喜欢成为一名企业家。我喜欢归零的感觉，就像站在原点一样。忘记你过去所做的一切。忘记别人对你的看法。只是埋头苦干，努力建设。”</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">AI研究的学术定位：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">“作为一名博士生，我建议你寻找那些并非与工业界存在冲突的‘北极星’问题，工业界能够利用更好的计算能力、更好的数据和团队科学来更好地解决这些冲突问题。”</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border: none;height: 1px;color: inherit;margin: 2em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));\">\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">ImageNet的诞生与深度学习的黎明</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">时间回到2007年左右，当时的李飞飞还在普林斯顿大学担任助理教授。彼时的人工智能领域，数据稀缺，算法效能不彰，神经网络被视为过时。但李飞飞和她的学生们，凭借对机器学习“泛化问题”的深刻理解，做出了一个大胆的战略性赌注：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我们必须赌机器学习需要一个范式转变，而且这个范式转变必须由数据驱动的方法来领导。”</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">这个赌注的产物就是ImageNet。他们从互联网上下载了数十亿张图片，并创建了一个涵盖全球视觉分类的庞大数据库，旨在训练和评估机器学习算法。尽管在最初的三年里，成果寥寥，但李飞飞团队坚持开源并举办挑战赛，吸引全球最顶尖的研究人员参与。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">历史的转折点出现在2012年。杰弗里·辛顿（Geoffrey Hinton）的团队（名为SuperVision）在ImageNet挑战赛中，凭借卷积神经网络（CNN）和GPU的算力结合，取得了突破性的进展。李飞飞回忆道：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“这是一个非常非常突出的结果，你应该看看。这是数据、GPU和神经网络结合在一起的最初时刻。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;ImageNet挑战赛的成功，不仅验证了数据驱动方法的巨大潜力，也预示着深度学习时代的全面到来，彻底改变了计算机视觉乃至整个AI领域的发展轨迹。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">从物体识别到场景叙事：视觉智能的演进</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">ImageNet的成功解决了物体识别这一视觉智能的根本问题。但对李飞飞而言，她的“一生梦想”远不止于此。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">她解释道，人类的视觉能力超越了简单的物体识别，能进行复杂的</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">场景故事叙述</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。当我们进入一个房间，我们看到的不只是独立的物体，而是一个有屏幕、舞台、观众和摄像头的会议室——一个完整的、有意义的场景。这种理解世界并与之互动的能力，是人类视觉智能的基石。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">当深度学习浪潮兴起，自然语言与视觉开始碰撞时，李飞飞和她的学生们，包括安德烈·卡帕西（Andrej Karpathy），提出了“图像描述”或“故事讲述”的问题。到2015年左右，他们发表的论文系列，使得计算机首次能够描述图像内容。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我当时几乎觉得，我这辈子该干什么呢？那是我毕生的目标。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;李飞飞感慨道。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">如今，随着生成式AI的爆发，从文字生成图像已成为现实，这在几年前是不可想象的。李飞飞认为，她有幸见证并参与了AI从“寒冬”到“腾飞”的整个过程，并为此深感骄傲。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">下一个前沿：空间智能与World Labs的创立</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">在实现了“场景叙事”这一“毕生梦想”之后，李飞飞并没有止步。她将目光投向了更宏大、更根本的挑战：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“空间智能”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。为此，她离开了学术界，创办了World Labs，一家旨在解决当前AI领域最困难问题的初创公司。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">李飞飞的灵感来源于对进化的思考。她指出，人类语言的进化历程不过数百万年，而对三维世界的理解、交互、导航和生成能力，在生物进化中却耗费了5.4亿年。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“从根本上说，语言是一维的……世界远比这复杂。首先，真实世界是3D的。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;她强调，三维世界的复杂性、感知过程中的投影难题以及真实世界与生成世界之间的转换，都使得空间智能成为比语言模型更具挑战性的领域。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">她指出，理解三维世界对于通用人工智能（AGI）的实现至关重要：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“对我来说，没有空间智能的通用人工智能（AGI）是不完整的。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;为此，她召集了一支“超级精英团队”，包括Pulsar的创造者克里斯·拉斯纳（Christoph Lassner）、神经风格迁移先驱贾斯汀·约翰逊（Justin Johnson）以及NERF论文作者本·米尔登霍尔（Ben Mildenhall），共同构建</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">全新的基础模型，其输出将是3D世界。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">World Labs的应用场景广阔，从创意设计（设计师、建筑师、艺术家）到机器人学习，再到营销、娱乐乃至元宇宙。李飞飞对元宇宙的未来充满兴奋，她认为一旦硬件和软件融合，并解决了内容创作的核心难题，它将释放巨大潜力。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">企业家精神：从洗衣店到AI研究院</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">对许多人来说，李飞飞从顶尖学者到科技公司CEO的转变可能显得突然，但对她而言，这不过是其人生轨迹中“归零”精神的延续。她分享了自己不平凡的成长经历——作为移民少年来到美国，一句英语都不会说，并在19岁时出于绝望开办了一家自助洗衣店，支撑家庭并资助自己进入普林斯顿大学。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我只是喜欢成为一名企业家。我喜欢归零的感觉，就像站在原点一样。忘记你过去所做的一切。忘记别人对你的看法。只是埋头苦干，努力建设。那是我的舒适区，我就是喜欢那样。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;李飞飞说道。这种敢于从零开始、专注于建设的韧性，贯穿了她的整个职业生涯，从选择在计算机视觉领域开辟新径的教授生涯，到在谷歌云学习商业，再到在斯坦福大学内部创办以人为本人工智能研究院（HAI），直至今天的World Labs。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">在培养和选择人才方面，李飞飞尤其看重一种特质：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“智识上的无畏。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;她强调，这是一种“</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">拥抱困难的无畏精神，并着手去做，全身心投入，以任何你想要的方式去解决它，这确实是成功人士的核心特征。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">” 她认为，无论是从事学术研究还是投身创业，这种敢于面对极其困难、近乎“妄想”问题的勇气，都是成功的关键。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">AI的未来：挑战、机遇与人类的角色</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">在问答环节，李飞飞对AI研究的未来方向给出了独到建议。她指出，如今学术界不再拥有像工业界那样庞大的计算和数据资源，因此博士生应将目光投向那些</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">并非与工业界存在冲突的‘北极星’问题</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，例如跨学科AI研究、理论层面如可解释性和因果关系，以及小数据等尚未被大规模计算能力覆盖的领域。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">对于通用人工智能（AGI）的定义，李飞飞持审慎态度，认为它与AI的最初愿景并无本质区别，都旨在创造能像人类一样甚至更智能地思考和做事的机器。至于AI的开源模式，她认为应保持多元健康，保护开源生态对创业和公共部门都至关重要。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">最后，当被问及作为少数群体在STEM领域面临的挑战时，李飞飞强调，每个人都有感到自己是“少数人”或“房间里唯一一个”的时刻。她的经验是：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">不要过度关注这一点……专注于去做就好。通过梯度下降法，让自己达到最优解</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这份务实的智慧，正是她不断追逐AI“北极星”的内在动力，也是她在技术浪潮中始终保持清醒和前行的关键。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">结语 | 全文传送</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">李飞飞博士的职业生涯，是一部不断突破自我、挑战既定边界的奋斗史。从ImageNet的数据播种，到场景叙事的故事讲述，再到如今对三维世界“空间智能”的雄心勃勃，她始终瞄准着AI领域最核心、最艰难的问题。她的故事不仅是关于技术革新，更是关于人类精神中那种对未知的好奇、对困难的无畏以及对建设的热爱。在AI迅速发展的当下，她所定义的“智识上的无畏”和“归零”的创业心态，或许正是指引我们走向未来的“北极星”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIxODUzNTg2MA==&amp;mid=2247488678&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=f6d990b71d8c45e9f8bc9e56ec2f4ebc&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【全文版】李飞飞最新YC现场访谈：从ImageNet到空间智能，追逐AI的北极星| 万字全文+视频\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【全文版】李飞飞最新YC现场访谈：从ImageNet到空间智能，追逐AI的北极星| 万字全文+视频</a></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;color: rgb(10, 10, 10);font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 0px;line-height: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "李飞飞博士分享从 ImageNet 到空间智能的研究历程，阐述 AI 未来发展方向，并展现其'智识无畏'的企业家精神。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "李飞飞博士分享从 ImageNet 到空间智能的研究历程，阐述 AI 未来发展方向，并展现其'智识无畏'的企业家精神。",
  "summary": "文章详细记录了李飞飞博士在 YC 创业学院的最新访谈内容。她回顾了 ImageNet 项目如何通过数据驱动方法与 GPU 算力、神经网络结合，引领深度学习革命。当前她聚焦的空间智能研究——构建理解和交互三维世界的能力，认为这对实现 AGI 至关重要。李飞飞分享了她从学术界转向创业 World Labs 的心路历程，强调'智识上的无畏'和'归零'的企业家精神。文章还探讨了 AI 研究的未来方向，包括跨学科研究、理论探索和保持开源生态多样性。",
